{"tid":481661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習權時代】「排華」蔓延 寧波爆炸後啟動清理低端人口","createTime":"2017-11-27T11:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T12:23:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07273f52f408f565fa08b7f6701f9f4da9bbfe86","tid":481661,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171127/large/1511772304_572c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171127%2Flarge%2F1511772304_572c.jpg&h=48929330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平親信、北京市委書記蔡奇，借大興區大火推動的強趕低端人口行動，已經在內地蔓延！浙江省寧波市委副書記、市長裘東耀下令，全市進行公共安全大檢查，以「鐵的紀律、鐵的手腕、鐵的決心」，重點清理分租房屋、待拆遷地區。有網民指，隨着各大城市開展清理低端人口行動，這將是中國境內最大規模的「排華行動」。<br />\n<br />\n寧波本地的媒體報道，裘東耀在爆炸發生後，昨下舉行全市安全工作視訊會議，要求全面深入開展公共安全、安全生產大檢查。其中「分租房屋、待拆遷地區」是檢查重點，要求官員「整治安全隱患」。<br />\n<br />\n類似的命令，與北京市在大興火後發出的命令，數以萬計的外地勞工已經被趕離居所，無家可，或是被趕回原居地。預計寧波的低端人口，將會面臨類似命運。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171127/57511411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171127%2F57511411&d=2CcPM0vuG8RefkPM5DztOr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=def29277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171127%2F57511411&h=cb01fcda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171127/57511411</a>"},{"pid":"4f57cdfaa14dc4eaeea60f578da45db46fa68cf5","tid":481661,"uid":83344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"共產黨對中國人最唔會手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}